data.description: POSSIBLE LOAN ASSUMPTION- Current loan is a VA loan and it may be assumable with a VA eligible buyer/loan, current interest rate is under 3%. Beautifully maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath home on a full basement.  Desirable schools! New hardwood flooring throughout home, new tile in bathrooms, freshly painted home. Brand new architecture shingled roof. Split bedroom plan with oversized owner's bedroom on main. Owner's bath has two sinks, jetted soaking tub, and separate shower with a large closet. Guest bedrooms on the far side of the home. Large guest bathroom with new tile floors. Full basement that can be finished out. Beautifully landscaped and maintained yard that backs up to a creek. Endless hours of outdoor time and play. Plenty of space for a garden, and for out door entertaining. Bring the friends over and enjoy the above ground pool just in time for pool season!
